ass=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Стоимость</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span><img alt=\"Иконка Гейм Золото\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/baldursgate/images/b/ba/%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%97%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BE.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/18?cb=20210131171215&amp;path-prefix=ru\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Иконка Гейм Золото.png\" data-image-key=\"%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%97%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BE.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" /></span></span> 10</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color pi-collapse pi-collapse-open\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Характерное</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"Дистанция боя\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Дистанция боя</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Ближний бой</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"Дальность\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Дальность</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">1,5 м</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<table class=\"pi-horizontal-group\">\n\t\n\t\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<th class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-label pi-secondary-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"Урон\">Урон</th>\n\t\t\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"Урон\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span><img alt=\"Иконка Кубик 1d4\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Иконка Кубик 1d4.png\" data-image-key=\"%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%9A%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%B8%D0%BA_1d4.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/baldursgate/images/7/71/%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%9A%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%B8%D0%BA_1d4.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/24?cb=20210318212024&amp;path-prefix=ru\" /></span></span> <span style=\"color:#aaaaaa\">1d4 <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span><img alt=\"Иконка Стат Дробящее\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Иконка Стат Дробящее.png\" data-image-key=\"%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%A1%D1%82%D0%B0%D1%82_%D0%94%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%8F%D1%89%D0%B5%D0%B5.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/baldursgate/images/0/09/%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%A1%D1%82%D0%B0%D1%82_%D0%94%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%8F%D1%89%D0%B5%D0%B5.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/16?cb=20210817232858&amp;path-prefix=ru\" /></span></span> Дробящее</span></td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n</p>\n<div style=\"margin-top:1em\">\n<div style=\"display: block\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span><img alt=\"Иконка Гейм Дневник\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Иконка Гейм Дневник.png\" data-image-key=\"%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%94%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/baldursgate/images/b/b3/%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%94%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20210724193634&amp;path-prefix=ru\" /></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Kurale; font-style:italic; margin-left: 36px; margin-top: -28px; border-left: 2px ridge #4a4a4a; padding-left: 10px\">Ветка дерева источает сильный смолистый запах.</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"font-style:italic; font-size:14px; padding-right:50px; color:lightcoral; text-shadow:1px 1px 2px #222, -1px 1px 2px #222, -1px -1px 2px #222, 1px -1px 2px #222; text-align:right; margin-bottom:2em\">Описание в игре</div>\n<p><b>Факел: кладбищенский синий</b> (англ. <i>Cemetery-Blue Torch</i>) — дубинка в <a href=\"/ru/wiki/Baldur%27s_Gate_III\" title=\"Baldur&#39;s Gate III\">Baldur's Gate III</a>.\n</p><p>Факел является предметом, который можно использовать и как источник света, и, одновременно, как импровизированное оружие-дубинку. Этот факел излучает синий свет.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\".D0.A3.D1.80.D0.BE.D0.BD\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Урон\">Урон</span></h2>\n<ul><li><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/baldursgate/images/7/71/%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%9A%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%B8%D0%BA_1d4.png/revision/latest?cb=20210318212024&amp;path-prefix=ru\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Иконка Кубик 1d4\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Иконка Кубик 1d4.png\" data-image-key=\"%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%9A%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%B8%D0%BA_1d4.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/baldursgate/images/7/71/%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%9A%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%B8%D0%BA_1d4.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20210318212024&amp;path-prefix=ru\" /></a></span> 1d4 (1~4) + (Модификатор силы) <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a hre